smalani530.shapes

Class Shape

  • java.lang.Object
    • smalani530.shapes.Shape
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Circle, Line, Rectangle

    public abstract class Shape
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a superclass for Rectangle, Line, and Circle. It contains the methods that all these shapes share.
    Version:
    10/10/2018
    Author:
    Sean Malani
